# Soft-to-loud arpeggio using VOL offsets on held notes.
# Useful for hearing row-to-row gain changes without changing pitch.

C4 VOL E0
--- VOL F0
--- VOL 00
--- VOL 10
E4 VOL F0
--- VOL 00
--- VOL 10
--- VOL 20
G4 VOL E0
--- VOL F0
--- VOL 00
--- VOL 10
C5 VOL 20
--- VOL 10
--- VOL 00
--- VOL F0
G4 VOL 10
--- VOL 00
E4 VOL F0
--- VOL E0
C4 VOL 00
--- VOL F0
OFF VOL E0
